</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
The spread between strongest and weakest currencies in the EMS grid narrowed
during the week, although the order of currencies was unchanged. The
Bundesbank council met and left German rates untouched. Earlier in the week
four French commercial banks had raised interest rates by 25 basis points.
