    P3724 Aircraft Engines and Engine Parts.
    P3728 Aircraft Parts and Equipment, NEC.
    P3761 Guided Missiles and Space Vehicles.
    P3769 Space Vehicle Equipment, NEC.
</IN>
<XX>
Types:-
</XX>
<TP>CMMT  Comment &amp; Analysis.
    COMP  Mergers &amp; acquisitions.
</TP>
<PUB>The Financial Times
</PUB>
